title: Sheet Music Watch Face
summary: An elegant & stylish watch face to show your love of music
description: With 8 different backgrounds to choose from, ranging from a classic bright sheet music style, to a futuristic blue neon glow, this is the perfect way to show off your love of music whilst making your smart watch look fantastic.The dark themes are particularly good if you have a watch with a chin / flat tyre, like the Moto 360.Please note, that it may take a couple of minutes to sync through to your smart watch once you have installed it on your phone.You can change your watch face theme by long clicking on the face and then selecting the settings cog.Enjoy :)
descriptionHTML:
With 8 different backgrounds to choose from, ranging from a classic bright sheet music style, to a futuristic blue neon glow, this is the perfect way to show off your love of music whilst making your smart watch look fantastic.

The dark themes are particularly good if you have a watch with a chin / flat tyre, like the Moto 360.

Please note, that it may take a couple of minutes to sync through to your smart watch once you have installed it on your phone.

You can change your watch face theme by long clicking on the face and then selecting the settings cog.

Enjoy :)
recentChanges: Increased the number of supported devices
